{
  "texts": [
    "By leveraging their inherent capabilities in reasoning and contextual understanding, these models can be guided to perceive and respond to user input, exhibiting goal-oriented behavior [97].",
    "For example, Shen et al. [98] proposed Data Director to automatically create data videos.",
    "In the Data Director system, GPT-4 was utilized as an intelligent agent to generate narrative text that established logical connections between data facts.",
    "Specifically, the system placed the GPT-4 in the role of a data analyst.",
    "By following a chain-of-thought approach, carefully designed prompts guide the GPT-4 to generate narrative text that not only connects insights into a coherent story but also ensures that the logic is compelling."
  ]
}